{"tid":2314732,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟son超越到曼連前輩朴智星未","createTime":"2020-12-06T17:35:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T08:41:17.000Z","uid":335956,"like":16,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"c2fb2112ca0d0625b15c074a68a98fa69d68b5de","tid":2314732,"uid":335956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T17:35:23.000Z","msg":"我認為都係未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02613e0e76d51e7bc2ab9f662b88055c1962fc9b","tid":2314732,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T23:38:23.000Z","msg":"未"},{"pid":"312dc4222cde35d28274b3658b875580b9f73663","tid":2314732,"uid":4917,"like":44,"dislike":2,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T00:17:53.000Z","msg":"未，除非佢去曼聯"},{"pid":"0f8df973a347d20c4b7bb88f8c5ed6a907ee28de","tid":2314732,"uid":149955,"like":23,"dislike":3,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T05:35:38.000Z","msg":"睇下點定義超越<br />\n<br />\n如果係計拎英超冠軍，其實有d唔公平，咁朴果時都唔算最carry 個個，但依家son係呢頭10周係英超第一人<br />\n<br />\n我覺得能力上，計rating 應該超越左好多<br />\n計成就就未算<br />\n<br />\n利申 曼迷+朴迷"},{"pid":"3b13cccf81e2dc5f522a8df30d93b94ce29ee80f","tid":2314732,"uid":186071,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T05:42:02.000Z","msg":"進攻一定過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果som係白人 今年應該去左皇馬"},{"pid":"1cc5b5c4e136c818529a1150fdb959bf9f360aa1","tid":2314732,"uid":31215,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T05:45:27.000Z","msg":"普遍人類貴古賤今<br />\n到今時今日都有人話朗拿度勁過美斯知咩料啦<br />\n我諗son 要4-50歲先有力同星仔一戰"},{"pid":"beb83a38d9fb1b82355595c30048d7a75be6eb1b","tid":2314732,"uid":54076,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T05:52:22.000Z","msg":"隻抽隻計 一定SON勁啲<br />\n但係時代唔同 當年啲亞洲人都冇而家咁勁咁多機會<br />\n咁以當時去計 佢會俾其他人亞洲球員/韓國人勁好多<br />\n咁佢嘅地位好自然就會特別突出"},{"pid":"f32d88ce63372fe7c9e39b4db4485f06ab25ec7b","tid":2314732,"uid